{"tid":1056726,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人有興趣學手風琴 (Accordion)?","createTime":"2019-03-11T11:35:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T11:37:19.000Z","uid":213556,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"8d100cab3319b0c4aae9a00623d6429b4bf04643","tid":1056726,"uid":213556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T11:35:14.000Z","msg":"有冇人有興趣學手風琴?<br />\n<br />\n香港冇乜人教, 老師質素參差, 學費亦唔平. (上網Search下 accordion hk 就會明白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />). 小弟回流香港幾月, 一直有跟開法國老師學琴, 有同另一位朋友係香港一齊玩手風琴. 但小弟已經有份好工, 唔想花太多時間教琴.不過小弟太鐘意呢種樂器, 覺得香港太少人玩, 好想將佢帶俾更多人一齊玩. 所以想睇下有幾多人有興趣, 然後想以一個極之合理價錢, 令更多人可以玩呢種樂器. 可能每星期日見一次面, 輕鬆一齊學, 小弟做過大學Lecturer, 中英教都得. 開始時可能想有音樂底既一 group人一齊學, 如果夠多人學, 之後可能請一位法國老師去香港教, 然後間唔中一齊Jam下歌.<br />\n<br />\n不過, 乜野係手風琴?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n手風琴有好多種, 比較簡單而常見既有Diatonic accordions, 呢種琴好輕, 主要用來玩folk songs 但音域細, 拉推個音不同(好似口琴). (呢種小弟冇學)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i9tcX5R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi9tcX5R.jpg&h=c0c5de5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另一種, 係全世界(除左法國) 較受歡迎既 piano accordion, 呢種琴6-15kg, 乜歌都玩得, 右手同鋼琴一樣, 但大細聲控制同鋼琴唔同, 拉推係同一個音. 缺點係有時要屈住右手彈, 琴制手感唔同鋼琴<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之後兩種係button accordion, 下個post再講<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rom90mk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2From90mk.jpg&h=dab88c02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6S1ufUG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6S1ufUG.jpg&h=7577df45&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"71b4678e5d5ab82fc49d7dcaca0fe759e6b6837e","tid":1056726,"uid":113136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T12:57:29.000Z","msg":"想請教下拉推有冇咩技巧?"},{"pid":"67cb62c87158ea9ed94458daa686caea12014569","tid":1056726,"uid":178484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T13:05:51.000Z","msg":"清有tg乎????"},{"pid":"18f9aa3dedb37fdf9ac3bf8557a8b2d206b3b664","tid":1056726,"uid":175651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T14:33:56.000Z","msg":"留名想學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有敲擊底(中學雞時期)<br />\n屋企得幾碌棍冇琴/鼓 想練都冇得練<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想學多樣樂器同人夾吓<br />\n<br />\n希望開得成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"109ac0330f28e4843e24f14157f65f2a4ccc5b92","tid":1056726,"uid":213556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"71b4678e5d5ab82fc49d7dcaca0fe759e6b6837e","tid":1056726,"uid":113136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T12:57:29.000Z","msg":"想請教下拉推有冇咩技巧?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T15:51:21.000Z","msg":"有,好多, 個Bellow係成件樂器既心臟, 用黎控制expression, phrasing, 推拉技巧對表演有好大影響"},{"pid":"dd6dbc6416ba8298c2430a90a924fc41138dae6f","tid":1056726,"uid":213556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"67cb62c87158ea9ed94458daa686caea12014569","tid":1056726,"uid":178484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T13:05:51.000Z","msg":"清有tg乎????"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T15:52:50.000Z","msg":"而家download番<br />\nid: accordeonhk"},{"pid":"338c2a60c61f9acec24bd06982791b16b6188f02","tid":1056726,"uid":178484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd6dbc6416ba8298c2430a90a924fc41138dae6f","tid":1056726,"uid":213556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"67cb62c87158ea9ed94458daa686caea12014569","tid":1056726,"uid":178484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T13:05:51.000Z","msg":"清有tg乎????"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T15:52:50.000Z","msg":"而家download番<br />\nid: accor