gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />). 小弟回流香港幾月, 一直有跟開法國老師學琴, 有同另一位朋友係香港一齊玩手風琴. 但小弟已經有份好工, 唔想花太多時間教琴.不過小弟太鐘意呢種樂器, 覺得香港太少人玩, 好想將佢帶俾更多人一齊玩. 所以想睇下有幾多人有興趣, 然後想以一個極之合理價錢, 令更多人可以玩呢種樂器. 可能每星期日見一次面, 輕鬆一齊學, 小弟做過大學Lecturer, 中英教都得. 開始時可能想有音樂底既一 group人一齊學, 如果夠多人學, 之後可能請一位法國老師去香港教, 然後間唔中一齊Jam下歌.<br />\n<br />\n不過, 乜野係手風琴?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n手風琴有好多種, 比較簡單而常見既有Diatonic accordions, 呢種琴好輕, 主要用來玩folk songs 但音域細, 拉推個音不同(好似口琴). (呢種小弟冇學)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i9tcX5R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi9tcX5R.jpg&h=c0c5de5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另一種, 係全世界(除左法國) 較受歡迎既 piano accordion, 呢種琴6-15kg, 乜歌都玩得, 右手同鋼琴一樣, 但大細聲控制同鋼琴唔同, 拉推係同一個音. 缺點係有時要屈住右手彈, 琴制手感唔同鋼琴<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之後兩種係button accordion, 下個post再講<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rom90mk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2From90mk.jpg&h=dab88c02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6S1ufUG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6S1ufUG.jpg&h=7577df45&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T17:44:06.000Z","msg":"至於Chromatic Button Accordion (CBA), 唔好俾D黑白制嚇親, 因為絕大部分時間, 只會彈外面數入去 頭3排制, 第4, 5排同第1, 2 排係一樣既. 右手白色同黑色制相等鋼琴黑白色制. 因為個制細D, 通常CBA音域會闊少少, 標準意大利CBA琴有46個 treble keys, 法國CBA琴更會去到56個, 計埋簧片組合, 最多可以加到80個treble keys! (即係只少普通鋼琴8個keys!) 相比一下, 標準piano accordion (PA)通常只有41個treble keys, 加埋簧片組合, 可以去到65個音. 另外, CBA係少數適合手細人士玩既樂器, 因為正常女人手要彈2個Octaves (16度)冇乜難度, 而且CBA多數會短身d, 彈最高/最低音時會順手d.<br />\n<br />\n咁點解世界上大部分人會鐘意彈PA多d?<br />\n1. CBA右手彃Chord難學<br />\n2. 通常CBA同型號比較貴d (因為多D簧片.音)<br />\n3. 識彈鋼琴學PA容易上手<br />\n4. CBA個琴好多時會肥D, 出聲未必會好同步, 同PA比, 有d人會選擇 PA (亦有人鐘意CBA聲音多d)<br />\n<br />\n咁學CBA定PA好? 兩種琴都有出色既音樂家用, 每個人都有唔要Preference, 我兩種都玩, 但個人鐘意CBA多D, 但有D 種類既歌 (eg 有d jazz)用PA易彈D<br />\n<br />\nTo further confuse you<br />\nCBA係有分兩大種- B system 同 C system (仲有其他種類, 在此不提.....). 好多人會識彈Piano accordion 加其中一種CBA, 但99%人係唔會識彈晒 B-system同 C-system. 至於選擇邊種, 好多時都係睇老師識彈邊種, 或者跟個人喜好.<br />\nC-system同B-system 有乜唔同? C-system 第1排音同第3排音倒轉左就係B-System. C system CBA= C音在最出一排, B system CBA= B音在最出一排, 呢個改變足以令彈唔同System既音樂家唔可以交換琴用. C-system係西歐 (法國, 意大利, 葡萄牙)極之普及, B-system係俄羅斯, Balkan states, 東歐前蘇聯國家, 北韓, 中國, (同Belgium老一輩)最為普及.<br />\n至於係香港, 有一個烏克蘭老師教B system CBA, 教C-System位老師已經去左澳門生活. 我同我朋友兩個正職都唔係音樂相關, 不過都係有玩C-system.<br />\n<br />\nC-System 最出一排有2個, 2個白色buttons<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LWkfden.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLWkfden.jpg&h=a033a538&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nB-System 最出一排有3個, 3個白色buttons<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EyK0pk2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEyK0pk2.jpg&h=2bc9cd2b&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果大家有興趣, 遲d會講下左手邊d制, 以及手風琴最精彩既一部分- tuning同埋唔同既聲音register.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外, 手風琴係世界上最難整既樂器, 一部琴拆開有幾千個Parts, 琴入面空間有限, 所以好多野都要量度得好準確. 即使到呢個年代, 手風琴好多部分依然係人手做, 一部標準大細既琴入面有四百幾塊簧片, 每塊Tune 3分鐘都用你一星期時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 所以一部簡單既新琴通常要用3-4個月先整好.<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EZAVXSn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEZAVXSn.jpg&h=bcc1996d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sSB6j5J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsSB6j5J.jpg&h=71491ec8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n小弟去過意大利同法國學整琴,  了解唔同琴廠製琴工序, 維修過大大小小既琴, 有時間既話再同同大家講解一下各品牌特色, 同埋講下中國最高質素既琴究竟有幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />.<br />\n<br />\n我打中文字好好好好慢, 今晚告一段落!<br />\nBonne nuit! Ciao ciao! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9bbe3bc94ec0e31f817aa62bbe1f0c4c31486e4","tid":1056726,"uid":13331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T17:47:39.000Z","msg":"鐘意聽手風琴ge歌<br />\n但睇樣都知好難學,本身又唔識西樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c3719a3195f60edee42f6773d5456a55597bd7f","tid":1056726,"uid":88303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T17:57:30.000Z","msg":"Libertango好正 <br />\n第一次聽係guitar+口琴<br />\n第二次係聽兩公婆玩 係accordion+cello<br />\n<br />\n正到癲 accordion d聲勁好聽"},{"pid":"95810cd1252021bcd2aa4897a569e0ebe089b50b","tid":1056726,"uid":213556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T09:01:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K3mey5X.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK3mey5X.jpg&h=9ecb6d05&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tUkODA8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtUkODA8.jpg&h=a638d19d&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n題外話, 法國有人用手風琴設計左一種叫Accordina既樂器, 聲音有d似口琴, 但吹法好唔同,小弟覺得Accordina玩jazz好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86008fdfa3998d179d97812dd7768a7c38cbc9a9","tid":1056726,"uid":10783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T09:02:25.000Z","msg":"ching 買手風琴都好能貴 無琴點學呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4479c6c6f43892d5f4875e60f9b8f86e948cabc","tid":1056726,"uid":213556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"86008fdfa3998d179d97812dd7768a7c38cbc9a9","tid":1056726,"uid":10783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T09:02:25.000Z","msg":"ching 買手風琴都好能貴 無琴點學呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T10:07:10.000Z","msg":"點樣為之貴先？ 一部新既意大利初階琴二萬左右， 2手既意大利琴， 幾千蚊都有非常唔錯選擇。 手風琴愈多複雜設計就愈貴， 但複雜既琴器唔一定聲靚， 而且愈複雜就愈重，愈多野壞。識玩既一定買一部簡單而聲靚既琴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港既琴行一係就生劏學生，一係就冇相熟制琴廠， 你要邊部琴佢就用零售價幫你入貨，當然貴啦！ 經相熟琴廠買新琴個價同你自己去意大利落訂價錢差好遠好遠。另外，買新琴好處就係好多野可以customise, 例如tuning, 琴制鬆緊etc. 不過好多有錢學生比左錢就唔理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，有d人連自己買緊乜都唔知。<br />\n<br />\n手風琴係世上最難整既樂器，整一部要幾個月，所以新琴一定比較貴。既然我開呢個post, 我當然考慮過呢問題。我自己有4部琴，可以畀你地玩。"},{"pid":"e64322714f8aa6bac4d91b9300e21bb644a0339b","tid":1056726,"uid":213556,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8c3719a3195f60edee42f6773d5456a55597bd7f","tid":1056726,"uid":88303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T17:57:30.000Z","msg":"Libertango好正 <br />\n第一次聽係guitar+口琴<br />\n第二次係聽兩公婆玩 係accordion+cello<br />\n<br />\n正到癲 accordion d聲勁好聽"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T10:09:37.000Z","msg":"真係好多人為libertango 而學手風琴<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3342123d4e8a96b213b5aac944a96bbd8a09b2e","tid":1056726,"uid":213556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5c96e3b0e2fce1e41396c4816f365b1e0b3790d1","tid":1056726,"uid":40908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T16:50:38.000Z","msg":"好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前有諗過學但真係好貴<br />\n樓主識唔識&lsquo;彈&rsquo;（定係用拉呢個字）哈爾移動城堡首歌？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可惜宜家我去左學鋼琴<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T10:12:01.000Z","msg":"之前同人係香港錄過呢首歌，但已經唔記得點彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n學鋼琴都可以玩手風琴，對piano accordion 仲會有好大幫助"},{"pid":"1544609862724216183923e5ac0ac6bacf1eee01","tid":1056726,"uid":113136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T13:37:52.000Z","msg":"平時有玩開口琴, 對手風琴都有啲興趣, 同埋想比較下兩者嘅聲音 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef0fcfd03621cddaceddb2d9b8f84e35986307cc","tid":1056726,"uid":213556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1544609862724216183923e5ac0ac6bacf1eee01","tid":1056726,"uid":113136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T13:37:52.000Z","msg":"平時有玩開口琴, 對手風琴都有啲興趣, 同埋想比較下兩者嘅聲音 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T05:44:17.000Z","msg":"聲音其實好唔同<br />\n手風琴特別之處, 就係一部琴自己會有唔同既聲音<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ws1uuAm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWs1uuAm.jpg&h=82d8ade7&s={SIZE}\" />  <br />\n琴上面有D制, 係可以模仿唔同聲音<br />\n如果一部琴右手有晒低, 中, 高音簧片, 同一個Key可以彈埋高8度或者低8度, 呢d制啟動唔同高低音簧片組知, 而做成唔同聲音效果<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Iht1CjxKiz8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DIht1CjxKiz8&d=JC%2BoF4fRaZyKvWcl7nla%2FKWONrq76Y1XZ%2F%2BBeLOBzgc%3D&h=cefbf967\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Iht1CjxKiz8</a><br />\n有d琴有2組中音簧片, 然後其中一組簧片 tune flat/ sharp左, 而做成tremolo/ beats, 至於點tune, tune幾多係另一門高深學問. 我地用wet同 dry 去形容唔同程度 detuning, wet 即係detune 得勁d, 聽落去會好似走左音咁, 比較 Wet 有呢個例子, 呢d聲比較多用黎彈 scottish folk, french cafe musette<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4yX291SkgEI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D4yX291SkgEI&d=JC%2BoF4fRaZyKvWcl7nla%2FKWONrq76Y1XZ%2F%2BBeLOBzgc%3D&h=37cc581f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4yX291SkgEI</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qcX7KEzPqe4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DqcX7KEzPqe4&d=JC%2BoF4fRaZyKvWcl7nla%2FKWONrq76Y1XZ%2F%2BBeLOBzgc%3D&h=67fd10d4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qcX7KEzPqe4</a><br />\n<br />\nDry tuned 即係冇Tremolo, 用黎彈jazz/ classical 較多<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-QiLac9MC6U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D-QiLac9MC6U&d=JC%2BoF4fRaZyKvWcl7nla%2FKWONrq76Y1XZ%2F%2BBeLOBzgc%3D&h=bba0755d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-QiLac9MC6U</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Vbik_9JPlmU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%